'''納亞帕拉難民營'''（{{lang-bn|নয়াপাড়া শরণার্থী শিবির}}）是[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]][[吉大港專區|吉大港專區]][[科克斯巴扎爾縣|科克斯巴扎爾縣]][[代格納夫烏帕齊拉|代格納夫烏帕齊拉]]的一個[[難民營|難民營]]。營地主要居民為因{{link-en|緬甸對穆斯林的迫害|Persecution of Muslims in Myanmar|宗教迫害}}而逃離[[緬甸|緬甸]]的[[罗兴亚人|罗兴亚人]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=The young and the hopeless in Bangladesh's camps|url=http://www.unhcr.org/news/latest/2013/1/50ffe3c29/young-hopeless-bangladeshs-camps.html|website=UNHCR|publisher=United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees|accessdate=2017-09-02|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220082044/https://www.unhcr.org/news/latest/2013/1/50ffe3c29/young-hopeless-bangladeshs-camps.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這是[[科克斯巴扎爾縣|科克斯巴扎爾縣]]內兩個官方難民營的其中一個，另一個是[[庫圖帕朗難民營|庫圖帕朗難民營]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Stories from the Rohingya Camps in Bangladesh|url=http://markjisaacs.com/displaced-people-of-asia/stories-rohingya-camps-bangladesh/|accessdate=2017-07-14|date=2016-09-05|language=en|archive-date=2018-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729203620/https://markjisaacs.com/displaced-people-of-asia/stories-rohingya-camps-bangladesh/|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2017年7月，庫圖帕隆和納亞帕拉的兩個難民營共有約30,000名登記難民。<ref>{{cite web|title=Two camps of thought on helping Rohingya in Bangladesh|url=http://www.unhcr.org/news/latest/2013/1/5106a7609/camps-thought-helping-rohingya-bangladesh.html|website=UNHCR|publisher=United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees|accessdate=2017-07-14|language=en|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926205439/https://www.unhcr.org/news/latest/2013/1/5106a7609/camps-thought-helping-rohingya-bangladesh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>到了2017年9月，[[联合国难民署|联合国难民署]]估計，兩個難民營的總人口增加到了77,000多人。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Judah|first1=Jacob|title=Rohingya influx strains camp resources in Bangladesh|url=http://www.unhcr.org/news/latest/2017/9/59ba9b7b4/rohingya-influx-strains-camp-resources-bangladesh.html|website=UNHCR|publisher=United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees|date=2017-09-15|accessdate=2017-10-04|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220082047/https://www.unhcr.org/news/latest/2017/9/59ba9b7b4/rohingya-influx-strains-camp-resources-bangladesh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{As of|2018|1|14}}，納亞帕拉難民營估計約有23,065人。<ref name="BBCJan25" />

2021年1月14日，難民營發生火災，導致約550個庇護所被燒毀。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-bangladesh-rohingya/fire-destroys-homes-of-thousands-in-rohingya-refugee-camps-unhcr-idUSKBN29J1AL |publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]] |title=Fire destroys homes of thousands in Rohingya refugee camps - UNHCR |date=2021-01-14 |first=Poppy Elena |last=McPherson |first2=Ruma |last2=Paul |editor-first=Simon |editor-last=Cameron-Moore |language=en |accessdate=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2021-01-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115185556/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-bangladesh-rohingya/fire-destroys-homes-of-thousands-in-rohingya-refugee-camps-unhcr-idUSKBN29J1AL |dead-url=no }}</ref>

